snippet.title: Legend of the Skyfish Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Arriving August 18th on iOS and Apple TV from Publisher Crescent Moon Games and developer MGaia Studios comes Legend of the Skyfish!

Little Red Hook is on an epic adventure to save her family!
Enjoy a wonderful hand-painted adventure for mobile devices.
